Class DirectionsStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxmaps.MapObject
      • com.teamdev.jxmaps.DirectionsStep
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class DirectionsStep
extends MapObject
    Represents directions step object. Contains a single DirectionsStep in a DirectionsResult. Some fields may be undefined.
